@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About MGI";
}

<!-- Page Header / Hero Section -->
<div class="page-header position-relative" style="background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 44, 95, 0.42), rgba(0, 44, 95, 0.46)), url('https://www.mgi.org/assets/images/about/a0.jpg') no-repeat center center; background-size: cover; padding: 120px 0; color: white;">
    <div class="container position-relative" style="z-index: 2;">
        <div class="text-center">
            <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold mb-3">About Meghna Group of Industries</h1>
            <p class="lead fs-4">Breaking Boundaries with 51 Years of Unstoppable Flow</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<section class="section-padding bg-light">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row align-items-center mt-2">
            <div class="col-lg-6 mb-2 mb-lg-0">
                <img src="~/img/loader.gif" class="img-fluid rounded shadow" alt="About MGI">
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <p class="lead">Meghna Group of Industries (MGI) is a prominent industrial conglomerate based in Bangladesh, recognized as one of the country's largest and leading business entities. The company's operations span a diverse array of sectors, playing a significant role in Bangladesh's economic landscape.</p>
                <p>MGI traces its roots back to 1976 with the establishment of Kamal Trading Company by Mostafa Kamal. The group officially became "Meghna Group" in the 1980s. The company is led by Mostafa Kamal, who serves as its Chairman and Managing Director. Its headquarters are located in Gulshan, Dhaka, Bangladesh.</p>
                <p>MGI operates over 57 industrial units and employs more than 65,000 individuals as of 2026. It also maintains a vast network of 6,650 distributors and 20,000 suppliers. The group's annual turnover is approximately $3.0 billion.</p>
                <p>With more than 51 years of national and global experience, Meghna Group of Industries is continuing to serve one in every two households in Bangladesh.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
